{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"7a52645f2f","title":"在刘少奇作反修报告时的插话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"696bd41f34","index":0,"year":1964,"month":9,"day":4,"articleId":"7a52645f2f","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"对外关系和政策","id":"2bffb53b5b","type":"主题"},{"name":"刘少奇","id":"3aaab89c2a","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"e2305b9e63","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"144f3aefc4","type":"title","text":"在刘少奇作反修报告时的插话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c6c1ab95df","type":"paragraph","text":"在刘少奇作反修报告时的插话","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da76813053","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"28e3d298cc","type":"paragraph","text":"1964. 09. 04","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"21775ea563","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：蛇是引出来好打，还是钻黑洞里好打？","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6b61d9cce0","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：对苏斯洛夫报告我们赞成发表，它不发。出了八评后引出来了。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"aa085d50fb","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：一九五六年以来，苏联骂斯大林，我们一论、二论发表后，他就失去了主动权。点名不光我们两家，东欧也点名了。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"46a484de3f","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：苏联批评罗自力更生，罗回击，用我们评苏联的话。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"da0d976251","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：不是内部的事，正在电台上干，公开干了。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c590c57b8","type":"paragraph","text":"控制、反控制的冲突，第一位的不是中国，而是东欧国家。","index":9,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"3dd7684d4d","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：罗已做了苏断绝经济关系的准备，自己不能制造武器，要求我国去人到罗访问，不讲话都可以使人震惊，去了不讲话，握握手都很重要。","index":10,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f510998947","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：中苏关系准备两手，准备破裂，争取拖。哪天出事，不要出于意料之外，天下大事，合久必分，分久必合。","index":11,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"fd307ba009","type":"paragraph","text":"刘：巴西老党四万人，成立新党六千人。","index":12,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5f5b0df447","type":"paragraph","text":"毛：是四万人可靠，还是六千人可靠？","index":13,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"021fbb9749","type":"paragraph","text":"南昌暴动轰轰烈烈，剩下不多人，以后发展了三十万人，长征剩下几万人，以后发展起来，山不在高。","index":14,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e0940c99db","type":"paragraph","text":"有了修正主义，列宁主义才能万岁！","index":15,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33c967e4ac","type":"paragraph","text":"不注意一定出修正主义，注意可能出可能不出；准备出，可能不出。","index":16,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"7a52645f2f","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}